---
import Container from "@/components/Container.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Link from "@/components/Link.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <Container>
    <div class="space-y-4 text-sm md:text-base relative z-10">
      <p class="leading-[150%] tracking-wide">
        i'm a full-stack engineer interested in building scalable and performant
        web applications. i enjoy crafting minimal user-interfaces using <Link
          className="md:text-base"
          blank={true}
          href="https://nextjs.org">Next.js</Link
        > and <Link
          className="md:text-base"
          blank={true}
          href="https://typescriptlang.org/">TypeScript</Link
        > with robust backend using <Link
          className="md:text-base"
          blank={true}
          href="https://orm.drizzle.team">DrizzleORM</Link
        > and <Link
          className="md:text-base"
          blank={true}
          href="https://turso.tech">Turso</Link
        > / <Link className="md:text-base" blank={true} href="https://neon.tech"
          >Neon</Link
        >.
      </p>
      <p class="leading-[150%] tracking-wide">
        im also keen about music, gfx and vfx. in the past i used to make AMVs
        to post on instagram (back in 2022), u may find some of my work <Link
          className="md:text-base"
          href="/archive"
          >here
        </Link>.
      </p>
      <p class="leading-[150%] tracking-wide">
        My goal is to build products that are easy to use and have a good UX -
        whether through building an app or writing code for other people (<Link
          className="md:text-base"
          href="/chat">hmu</Link
        > for freelance work).
      </p>

      <ul class="space-y-2.5 list-disc list-inside">
        <li>
          Built <Link
            className="md:text-base"
            blank={true}
            href="https://indielettr.com">IndieLettr</Link
          > - empowering indie creators and small businesses to reach their audience.
        </li>
        <li>
          Cooking <Link
            className="md:text-base"
            blank={true}
            href="https://papyrus.astro-dev.tech">Papyrus</Link
          > - note taking on steroids.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </Container>
</Layout>
